Gaps:
- Non-existent `bookId`/chapter number ‚Üí should return `null`.
- Chapter file with no `# Title` line ‚Üí falls back to `Chapter ${n}`.
- Chapter with no `## Key Ideas` / `## In Practice` sections ‚Üí both arrays empty, everything lands in body.
- Section headings with different casing (`## KEY IDEAS`) ‚Äî relies on `.toLowerCase()`.
- Bullets using `*` vs `-`.
- Word/minute math: `words / 220` rounding, and the `Math.max(3, ‚Ä¶)` floor for very short chapters.
- Two `## Key Ideas` blocks in one file (second one silently overwrites first, since `keyIdeas =` not `push`).

